NOILLY PRAT

We all know the excellence of NOILLY PRAT Extra Dry Vermouth from France—and now France sends us, for the first time, the superb Noilly Prat Sweet Vermouth. Noilly Prat is the classic dry French Vermouth by which all other Vermouths are judged. It is pale, extra dry, of impeccable origin, and renowned through the world. It is the ideal companion for the Dry Martini—also excellent on-the-rocks with a twist of lemon peel.

Its delightful counterpart-Noilly Prat Sweet Vermouth from France—is now available. You will be delighted with its fruity richness and beautiful balance. (36.18 case) Your Choice 3.35
